1
00:01:40,660 --> 00:01:42,000
=What If=

2
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:44,980
=What If=

3
00:01:44,980 --> 00:01:47,820
=Episode 2=
(Remain Or Leave)

4
00:01:58,480 --> 00:02:01,000
I never expected
the fall to be that severe.

5
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:04,710
Old people can't afford to fall.

6
00:02:04,714 --> 00:02:06,900
Once they fall,
all kinds of complications will arise.

7
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:09,771
What do you two plan to do?

8
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,550
Will you be heading to Shanghai first?

9
00:02:12,857 --> 00:02:14,742
I don't think we'll be able to make it.

10
00:02:14,914 --> 00:02:16,600
I don't dare to ask them about it too.

11
00:02:17,030 --> 00:02:18,280
Isn't your flight this Saturday?

12
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,600
Why are you still delaying it?

13
00:02:22,190 --> 00:02:25,400
But how can I tell them
at such a moment?

14
00:02:26,430 --> 00:02:28,520
Tell his sister to
help you guys out for now.

15
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:29,710
That won't do.

16
00:02:29,840 --> 00:02:31,080
His sister is in the U.S.

17
00:02:31,150 --> 00:02:32,000
She just got married.

18
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:33,520
There's no way she can come back.

19
00:02:35,310 --> 00:02:36,240
Guo,

20
00:02:37,030 --> 00:02:38,280
you must think it through.

21
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:41,080
You must prepare for the worst.

22
00:02:42,030 --> 00:02:43,190
Will you go

23
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:44,520
if Yu Jian isn't going?

24
00:02:53,285 --> 00:02:54,942
(I like how straightforward you are.)

25
00:02:55,170 --> 00:02:58,140
If this choice of yours will make you
lose everything you possess currently,

26
00:02:58,150 --> 00:02:59,428
(will you be able to accept it?)

27
00:03:00,150 --> 00:03:03,240
(I hope to see you in our Shanghai HQ
on the 1st of next month.)

28
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,400
I have to tell you this.

29
00:03:05,485 --> 00:03:08,560
You shouldn't jeopardize your career
because of someone else.

30
00:03:10,190 --> 00:03:10,960
Look at me.

31
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:11,960
I'm a great example.

32
00:03:12,870 --> 00:03:14,310
I got married very early.

33
00:03:14,590 --> 00:03:16,310
After that, I was shackled by my family.

34
00:03:17,430 --> 00:03:18,360
My bright future

35
00:03:18,590 --> 00:03:20,190
just passed by right in front of me.

36
00:03:21,310 --> 00:03:22,910
Do you know what's the worst about it?

37
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:25,910
No matter how great of a job
you're doing as a daughter-in-law,

38
00:03:25,920 --> 00:03:27,790
your other half will
always complain about you.

39
00:03:27,857 --> 00:03:29,485
He said I didn't serve his parents well

40
00:03:29,630 --> 00:03:30,870
or teach our child well.

41
00:03:31,630 --> 00:03:33,520
I wondered if I was
actually that incompetent

42
00:03:33,885 --> 00:03:35,742
and that I couldn't do anything right.

43
00:03:36,257 --> 00:03:37,771
That's why you should listen to me.

44
00:03:37,780 --> 00:03:40,590
When you encounter a situation,
don't think of making compromises first.

45
00:03:41,710 --> 00:03:43,120
No one can fulfill your goals.

46
00:03:43,571 --> 00:03:45,600
You're the only one
who can fulfill your goals.

47
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:01,030
You're here.

48
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:14,520
How's Mr. Yu doing?

49
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:15,942
I'm sure it still hurts, huh?

50
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:17,114
He just received a shot.

51
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,690
He's not complaining about the pain now.

52
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:22,480
It's just that he can't move or eat.

53
00:04:23,430 --> 00:04:24,480
He may feel terrible,

54
00:04:24,950 --> 00:04:26,190
but I feel worse looking at him.

55
00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:29,920
Have you eaten?

56
00:04:30,257 --> 00:04:31,342
You should have something.

57
00:04:32,314 --> 00:04:33,342
I have no appetite.

58
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:34,390
Have you eaten?

59
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:35,560
Yeah.

60
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:36,750
I had dinner with Ms. Ping.

61
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:38,560
Good.

62
00:04:39,870 --> 00:04:41,950
Guo, it's been a long day.

63
00:04:42,070 --> 00:04:42,950
Let me send you back.

64
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:44,270
I'm fine.

65
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:47,360
I won't be working tomorrow.

66
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:49,190
I've already done my job handover.

67
00:04:53,390 --> 00:04:54,120
Okay.

68
00:05:00,620 --> 00:05:01,620
(Dear Mr. Yu Jian:)

69
00:05:01,620 --> 00:05:02,620
(Dear Ms. Xia Guo:)

70
00:05:02,620 --> 00:05:05,057
(Welcome onboard to Flight Shuangliu,
Chengdu, - Hongqiao, Shanghai)

71
00:05:16,630 --> 00:05:18,240
Ms. Ping asked me this today.

72
00:05:18,857 --> 00:05:21,428
She asked me whether
I was still heading to Shanghai or not.

73
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:23,390
I said I hadn't
discussed it with you yet.

74
00:05:24,630 --> 00:05:25,870
Look at the state he's in.

75
00:05:28,750 --> 00:05:29,950
I hear that.

76
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:31,950
It's...

77
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:34,830
Guo, you're here, right?

78
00:05:35,070 --> 00:05:36,140
Mr. Yu, are you awake?

79
00:05:36,430 --> 00:05:37,480
It's me.

80
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:38,720
Come.

81
00:05:41,510 --> 00:05:42,360
Are you okay?

82
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:43,830
How do you feel?

83
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:49,070
Today, I feel much better.

84
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:51,160
I feel more energetic.

85
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:52,750
Guo,

86
00:05:53,510 --> 00:05:56,630
I wish to talk to you.

87
00:05:57,870 --> 00:05:59,190
Mr. Yu, what do you wish to say?

88
00:05:59,190 --> 00:06:00,680
Please go ahead. I'm listening.

89
00:06:02,270 --> 00:06:03,750
I'm very happy

90
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:06,870
that you're here to visit me.

91
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:07,680
It's my duty.

92
00:06:09,680 --> 00:06:11,430
I heard from Jian

93
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:14,480
that you were heading to Shanghai.

94
00:06:15,070 --> 00:06:16,310
I don't know

95
00:06:17,630 --> 00:06:19,510
when I'll be able to see you again.

96
00:06:19,750 --> 00:06:20,600
Guo.

97
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:23,480
Mr. Yu, it won't be long.

98
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:25,510
I can come back and visit you often.

99
00:06:25,750 --> 00:06:27,240
If you rest and recuperate,

100
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:28,720
I'm sure you'll recover soon.

101
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:31,750
By then, we can visit
great restaurants together, okay?

102
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:35,480
I hope that comes true.

103
00:06:36,070 --> 00:06:37,830
This may sound hilarious,

104
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:40,310
but I've never left Sichuan

105
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:42,600
ever since I was transferred to Leshan

106
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:45,600
from Northern China.

107
00:06:47,390 --> 00:06:49,360
Look at the state I'm in.

108
00:06:50,870 --> 00:06:52,480
Forget about leaving Sichuan,

109
00:06:54,510 --> 00:06:56,430
I don't even know if I could

110
00:06:58,480 --> 00:07:00,000
stand up and walk again.

111
00:07:00,310 --> 00:07:01,390
Mr. Yu, that won't be.

112
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:06,680
I've been thinking about this
for the past few days.

113
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:11,430
When people grow old,

114
00:07:12,950 --> 00:07:15,560
they have nothing to look forward to.

115
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:19,028
I would've taken my own life

116
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:21,720
had Jian not accompanied me

117
00:07:24,190 --> 00:07:26,160
all this while.

118
00:07:29,430 --> 00:07:33,040
I'm afraid I can't leave Jian's side.

119
00:07:45,060 --> 00:07:49,820
(Outpatient)

120
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:53,070
- You...
- You...

121
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:56,310
You can go first.

122
00:07:59,857 --> 00:08:01,257
Have you contacted our landlord?

123
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:03,360
Not yet.

124
00:08:03,830 --> 00:08:05,114
We can talk about it tomorrow.

125
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:09,630
What's on your mind?

126
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:12,830
I want to say

127
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:17,720
that if you no longer miss me...

128
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:22,560
What do you mean by that?

129
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:27,480
You see,

130
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:29,720
if you no longer miss me,

131
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:31,920
you mustn't pretend to miss me.

132
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,670
What nonsense are you talking about?

133
00:08:39,914 --> 00:08:42,828
You're letting your imagination run wild
even before you leave the place.

134
00:08:47,750 --> 00:08:48,390
Fine, then.

135
00:08:49,790 --> 00:08:53,550
If so, you must remember that I'm
missing you too when you're missing me.

136
00:08:54,550 --> 00:08:56,270
I'll wonder if you're starving,

137
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:57,750
if you're exhausted,

138
00:08:59,080 --> 00:09:02,120
if you slept without taking a bath,

139
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:04,857
or if you stayed up all night
just to play video games again.

140
00:09:05,670 --> 00:09:06,870
But who will keep me in check

141
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:10,600
when you're away?

142
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:13,000
Guo,

143
00:09:14,550 --> 00:09:15,670
can you please don't...

144
00:09:17,870 --> 00:09:18,840
What?

145
00:09:21,750 --> 00:09:22,600
Don't...

146
00:09:23,670 --> 00:09:24,790
Why did you stop halfway?

147
00:09:27,750 --> 00:09:28,870
I meant,

148
00:09:30,790 --> 00:09:32,630
can you call me more often

149
00:09:33,800 --> 00:09:35,857
and send me clips
of your daily life over there?

150
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:39,150
I know that.

151
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:40,630
Don't worry.

152
00:09:40,630 --> 00:09:42,000
I'll call you every day,

153
00:09:42,390 --> 00:09:43,200
okay?

154
00:09:44,150 --> 00:09:45,200
Be a good boy.

155
00:09:45,630 --> 00:09:47,790
Take good care of yourself
on my behalf, you hear me?

156
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:55,240
Both of us should eat well, work well,

157
00:09:56,085 --> 00:09:57,440
and take good care of ourselves.

158
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:11,240
Guo, I'm sorry.

159
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:13,390
I broke my promise.

160
00:10:14,510 --> 00:10:16,000
I can't go to Shanghai with you.

161
00:10:17,510 --> 00:10:18,480
I'm sorry.

162
00:10:18,790 --> 00:10:19,630
I understand.

163
00:10:20,150 --> 00:10:21,030
It's fine.

164
00:10:21,630 --> 00:10:23,390
Take good care of your parents.

165
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:26,080
Right now, they need you more than me.

166
00:10:27,030 --> 00:10:27,790
I'm fine.

167
00:10:28,120 --> 00:10:29,270
I'm truly fine.

168
00:10:37,700 --> 00:10:42,940
(Outpatient)

169
00:11:06,670 --> 00:11:07,270
Here.

170
00:12:33,180 --> 00:12:37,060
♪The laid-back lights in the city♪

171
00:12:37,460 --> 00:12:41,220
♪Warming the exhausted hearts♪

172
00:12:41,620 --> 00:12:45,180
♪The familiar back I remember♪

173
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:48,240
(Why would I head there without you?)

174
00:12:48,240 --> 00:12:49,080
(You must be joking.)

175
00:12:49,090 --> 00:12:50,670
Many people desire
to have a meal with you

176
00:12:50,680 --> 00:12:52,485
yet they don't have
the opportunity to do so.

177
00:12:53,980 --> 00:12:57,700
♪Spending my life with you only♪

178
00:12:58,020 --> 00:13:01,580
♪A wonderful life is inside my heart♪

179
00:13:01,980 --> 00:13:04,220
♪A simple song♪

180
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:07,200
(I just want to be someone ordinary.
Isn't it nice to be down-to-earth?)

181
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:07,910
To be with you.

182
00:13:10,420 --> 00:13:14,100
♪I want to be with you♪

183
00:13:14,940 --> 00:13:18,100
♪Are you also thinking of me♪

184
00:13:18,340 --> 00:13:22,380
♪When you're away?♪

185
00:13:24,428 --> 00:13:27,080
(Guo, the entire grade will head to
Shanghai for our summer camp)

186
00:13:27,080 --> 00:13:29,480
during summer break.
Do you wish to join me?

187
00:13:29,910 --> 00:13:30,840
I do wish to join you,

188
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:32,510
but we aren't in the same grade.

189
00:13:32,600 --> 00:13:33,440
How can I join you?

190
00:13:33,450 --> 00:13:34,790
I'll discuss it with our teachers.

191
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:35,790
I'll tell them...

192
00:13:35,800 --> 00:13:38,428
Your parents went on a business trip.
You're all alone at home.

193
00:13:39,150 --> 00:13:39,960
Will that work?

194
00:13:40,030 --> 00:13:40,600
Don't worry.

195
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:41,440
It'll work.

196
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:42,960
Dad!

197
00:13:43,390 --> 00:13:44,960
Dad, please don't leave!

198
00:13:45,630 --> 00:13:46,630
I'm begging you!

199
00:13:46,750 --> 00:13:48,000
Please don't leave!

200
00:13:54,150 --> 00:13:56,750
Guo, you should go back.

201
00:13:58,080 --> 00:13:59,440
Spend your days with your mother.

202
00:14:01,150 --> 00:14:02,000
I...

203
00:14:03,390 --> 00:14:06,550
Dad!

204
00:14:09,480 --> 00:14:11,630
Dad!

205
00:14:12,500 --> 00:14:16,460
♪Smoke vanishing from the window♪

206
00:14:17,630 --> 00:14:19,120
Guo? Guo, why are you crying?

207
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:20,120
I'm here, aren't I?

208
00:14:21,750 --> 00:14:23,870
Mom forced Dad to leave our family!

209
00:14:24,840 --> 00:14:25,960
I'm not going!

210
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:27,320
I'm not going to Shanghai!

211
00:14:27,390 --> 00:14:28,360
I'm not going anywhere!

212
00:14:28,360 --> 00:14:29,630
I want Dad to come back!

213
00:14:30,030 --> 00:14:30,720
Guo, don't cry.

214
00:14:30,730 --> 00:14:32,100
I'm not going to Shanghai either.

215
00:14:32,110 --> 00:14:33,520
I'll stay here and keep you company.

216
00:14:33,670 --> 00:14:34,550
I'll keep you company.

217
00:14:37,420 --> 00:14:41,020
♪So, you never left♪

218
00:14:41,260 --> 00:14:44,740
♪My world from the start♪

219
00:14:45,780 --> 00:14:49,300
♪I want to be with you♪

220
00:14:49,940 --> 00:14:53,460
♪I want to be with you♪

221
00:14:54,260 --> 00:14:57,420
♪Are you also thinking of me♪

222
00:14:57,540 --> 00:15:01,660
♪When you're away?♪

223
00:15:04,870 --> 00:15:05,720
Guo!

224
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:07,030
Guo!

225
00:15:10,500 --> 00:15:13,620
♪I yearned to tell you♪

226
00:15:14,180 --> 00:15:18,540
♪How lonely this city is♪

227
00:15:19,840 --> 00:15:20,840
Yam Head.

228
00:15:53,240 --> 00:15:54,000
I'm not leaving.

229
00:15:54,028 --> 00:15:55,371
I'll never leave your side again.

230
00:15:59,480 --> 00:16:01,840
(What's so bad about
living in a small circle?)

231
00:16:02,870 --> 00:16:04,440
(I'll execute my life perfectly)

232
00:16:04,510 --> 00:16:07,150
(and I'll lead a happy life.)

233
00:16:07,910 --> 00:16:08,720
(Because)

234
00:16:09,200 --> 00:16:11,670
(that's the life I will lead
together with Yu Jian.)

235
00:16:51,820 --> 00:16:56,740
(Four Years Later)

236
00:17:04,314 --> 00:17:05,657
It's falling out of your mouth.

237
00:17:06,270 --> 00:17:07,980
Chen is indeed a good boy.

238
00:17:08,000 --> 00:17:10,200
His fever subsided right after
taking the medicine, right?

239
00:17:10,200 --> 00:17:10,960
Is she right?

240
00:17:11,640 --> 00:17:12,270
Yu Jian,

241
00:17:12,480 --> 00:17:14,114
what time did you come back last night?

242
00:17:14,790 --> 00:17:15,790
Before 12 A.M.

243
00:17:16,160 --> 00:17:18,240
Jian, why did you come back so late?

244
00:17:18,510 --> 00:17:19,200
I was working.

245
00:17:20,480 --> 00:17:22,120
Today's the weekend.

246
00:17:22,440 --> 00:17:24,240
You should take your child out.

247
00:17:25,510 --> 00:17:26,160
Not today.

248
00:17:26,240 --> 00:17:27,580
I have to meet a client.

249
00:17:28,590 --> 00:17:29,440
Look at you.

250
00:17:29,680 --> 00:17:31,840
You're never home.

251
00:17:32,110 --> 00:17:35,160
You're treating our house like a hotel.

252
00:17:35,285 --> 00:17:36,380
(Wen Ya: I'm downstairs.)

253
00:17:40,485 --> 00:17:41,640
It's so early in the morning,

254
00:17:41,640 --> 00:17:43,160
yet he's always busy with work.

255
00:17:43,480 --> 00:17:44,440
Here, pass him to me.

256
00:17:44,720 --> 00:17:45,920
- Go and take a nap.
- Okay.

257
00:17:45,930 --> 00:17:47,120
Grandma will take care of you.

258
00:17:47,120 --> 00:17:49,660
It's fine. I'll go to the mall later
to buy some stuff for Chen.

259
00:17:50,070 --> 00:17:51,800
Yu Jian, did you hear her?

260
00:17:51,880 --> 00:17:53,240
Send Guo to the mall.

261
00:17:53,400 --> 00:17:54,350
Mom, it's okay.

262
00:17:54,510 --> 00:17:55,420
He's busy today.

263
00:17:55,590 --> 00:17:56,720
I can head there myself.

264
00:17:57,550 --> 00:17:58,440
Let's go.

265
00:17:58,440 --> 00:17:59,800
Do you want to ride your car?

266
00:18:10,960 --> 00:18:11,550
I'll drive.

267
00:18:11,571 --> 00:18:13,000
You're familiar with the area.

268
00:18:36,860 --> 00:18:38,980
(Lechuan Hotel)

269
00:18:54,857 --> 00:18:56,110
(Would I make the same choice)

270
00:18:56,110 --> 00:18:58,030
(if I knew this was the kind of life)

271
00:18:58,880 --> 00:19:00,640
(awaiting me in this small circle?)

272
00:19:01,510 --> 00:19:03,750
(Or would I choose
to depart to Shanghai?)

273
00:19:11,580 --> 00:19:12,860
(Employee ID)

274
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:14,771
(Marriage Certificate)

275
00:19:47,060 --> 00:19:58,460
(Shanghai)

276
00:20:31,170 --> 00:20:32,228
Hello. Your parcel is here.

277
00:20:32,350 --> 00:20:33,000
