How dare you pull such tricks?

546
00:33:32,070 --> 00:33:33,400
This shop is hard to order from.

547
00:33:33,400 --> 00:33:34,914
I couldn't order from them before this.

548
00:33:35,114 --> 00:33:35,830
How did you do it?

549
00:33:36,000 --> 00:33:38,780
I hired a delivery rider and paid him
extra to deliver the food to you.

550
00:33:38,860 --> 00:33:39,790
You must pay him a lot.

551
00:33:40,485 --> 00:33:42,510
There's no need to save up
this kind of money.

552
00:33:42,542 --> 00:33:45,000
After all, your craving is
more important than anything else.

553
00:33:45,010 --> 00:33:47,857
Tell me if you crave anything
in the future. I'll mail them to you.

554
00:33:48,880 --> 00:33:49,590
I'm craving you.

555
00:33:49,960 --> 00:33:51,340
Isn't our video call enough?

556
00:33:51,542 --> 00:33:54,210
If so, I have no choice but to fly
to your side as soon as possible.

557
00:33:54,314 --> 00:33:55,257
I'll wait for you, then.

558
00:33:57,070 --> 00:33:57,750
You're the best.

559
00:34:00,571 --> 00:34:02,400
Were you on the phone
with Xia Guo again?

560
00:34:02,550 --> 00:34:04,580
It's been a long day.
How can your body stand this?

561
00:34:04,590 --> 00:34:05,960
Mom, you scared me.

562
00:34:06,720 --> 00:34:07,880
I'm not exhausted. It's fine.

563
00:34:08,228 --> 00:34:09,771
What do you mean by you're fine?

564
00:34:10,710 --> 00:34:12,760
Is she still pestering you now?

565
00:34:14,000 --> 00:34:16,000
Listen, you shouldn't
keep in touch with her.

566
00:34:17,828 --> 00:34:20,571
She's my girlfriend.
Why shouldn't I keep in touch with her?

567
00:34:21,880 --> 00:34:23,030
Girlfriend?

568
00:34:23,800 --> 00:34:25,400
Don't be angry at me for saying this.

569
00:34:25,400 --> 00:34:26,670
But you spoiled her.

570
00:34:27,085 --> 00:34:28,714
She's not taking you seriously at all.

571
00:34:28,720 --> 00:34:30,060
When your father was hospitalized,

572
00:34:30,070 --> 00:34:32,140
I thought she could delay
her transfer to Shanghai.

573
00:34:32,457 --> 00:34:34,285
But she abandoned you
and left the place.

574
00:34:34,670 --> 00:34:35,230
Wait.

575
00:34:35,670 --> 00:34:37,030
What do you mean by that?

576
00:34:37,110 --> 00:34:38,440
I'll take care of my own father.

577
00:34:38,440 --> 00:34:39,914
She doesn't have
the obligation to stay.

578
00:34:39,920 --> 00:34:40,550
Yu Jian,

579
00:34:41,150 --> 00:34:42,190
I'm sure you know

580
00:34:42,200 --> 00:34:44,320
how your father and I
treated Xia Guo all these years.

581
00:34:44,630 --> 00:34:46,200
We treated her like our daughter.

582
00:34:46,630 --> 00:34:48,150
But she left us without saying a word.

583
00:34:48,550 --> 00:34:51,100
How can you marry her when
she's not sharing your woes with you?

584
00:34:51,110 --> 00:34:52,660
Just like her mom!

585
00:34:52,670 --> 00:34:53,670
That's enough.

586
00:34:53,800 --> 00:34:54,920
Alright, I got it.

587
00:34:55,000 --> 00:34:55,800
You should go home.

588
00:34:55,942 --> 00:34:57,371
I'm here to replace your shift.

589
00:34:57,710 --> 00:35:00,000
You pulled an all-nighter last night
and you worked today.

590
00:35:00,010 --> 00:35:01,285
You should head back and sleep.

591
00:35:02,100 --> 00:35:04,885
Alright, I'll keep my phone switched on.
Call me if you need anything.

592
00:35:06,320 --> 00:35:09,320
By the way, I think Ms. Liu

593
00:35:09,320 --> 00:35:10,428
looks like a nice girl.

594
00:35:10,710 --> 00:35:11,630
She's not married yet.

595
00:35:11,640 --> 00:35:12,914
Why don't you add her on WeChat?

596
00:35:13,030 --> 00:35:14,840
Mom, since when did you
get a hobby like this?

597
00:35:15,000 --> 00:35:15,800
You're so annoying.

598
00:35:16,100 --> 00:35:18,270
You'll regret it if you don't
listen to elderly people.

599
00:35:18,280 --> 00:35:19,150
Stop nagging me.

600
00:35:19,280 --> 00:35:22,060
Just listen to me. Buy some fruits
and deliver them to her tomorrow.

601
00:35:22,070 --> 00:35:22,840
You're so annoying.

602
00:35:23,030 --> 00:35:24,510
That hurts!

603
00:35:31,840 --> 00:35:32,440
Xia Guo,

604
00:35:32,880 --> 00:35:34,320
did you bring this chili sauce here?

605
00:35:35,670 --> 00:35:37,240
It's so delicious.

606
00:35:37,480 --> 00:35:38,480
Let me take a picture.

607
00:35:38,550 --> 00:35:39,880
I'll see if I can buy it later.

608
00:35:40,114 --> 00:35:41,100
You don't need to buy it.

609
00:35:41,130 --> 00:35:43,428
I have plenty of them.
You can have as much as you like.

610
00:35:43,885 --> 00:35:45,800
I don't think that's appropriate,
you know?

611
00:35:45,810 --> 00:35:46,950
I'll search for it first.

612
00:35:46,960 --> 00:35:49,057
If I can't find it,
I'll come and sponge off you.

613
00:35:49,085 --> 00:35:51,270
Don't stand on ceremony.
You can have it all you like.

614
00:35:51,590 --> 00:35:52,960
Xia Guo, you're so nice.

615
00:35:56,510 --> 00:35:57,630
What is this?

616
00:35:58,710 --> 00:35:59,760
Chili sauce?

617
00:35:59,800 --> 00:36:00,914
Whose chili sauce is this?

618
00:36:01,230 --> 00:36:02,000
It's Guo's.

619
00:36:02,320 --> 00:36:04,400
I'm taking its picture.
Can you return it to me?

620
00:36:06,000 --> 00:36:06,670
You want it back?

621
00:36:07,800 --> 00:36:08,920
Be nice to me, then.

622
00:36:10,280 --> 00:36:11,280
Larry.

623
00:36:11,630 --> 00:36:12,800
I can't hear you.

624
00:36:15,280 --> 00:36:16,000
Larry,

625
00:36:16,150 --> 00:36:17,880
can you return my chili sauce to me?

626
00:36:18,510 --> 00:36:19,440
Here you go.

627
00:36:22,920 --> 00:36:24,030
I'll stop teasing you.

628
00:36:26,710 --> 00:36:27,630
Your hand is so hot.

629
00:36:28,342 --> 00:36:29,685
Don't you think my hands are cold?

630
00:36:30,480 --> 00:36:31,230
Aren't they cold?

631
00:36:37,030 --> 00:36:39,670
Guo, the company's heater
is working as intended,

632
00:36:40,371 --> 00:36:41,800
yet you're wearing a sweater.

633
00:36:41,971 --> 00:36:43,320
It's a turtleneck sweater as well.

634
00:36:43,400 --> 00:36:44,190
Aren't you hot?

635
00:36:44,590 --> 00:36:45,480
Nope, not at all.

636
00:36:45,590 --> 00:36:46,590
I'm afraid of the cold.

637
00:36:46,828 --> 00:36:48,285
You're afraid of the cold?

638
00:36:50,360 --> 00:36:51,480
Look at our company.

639
00:36:51,514 --> 00:36:52,828
There are plenty of ladies here.

640
00:36:52,960 --> 00:36:54,920
Everyone is trying
to outdress one another.

641
00:36:55,590 --> 00:36:56,360
Look at you.

642
00:36:56,510 --> 00:36:58,000
If you're wearing this, it's obvious

643
00:36:58,000 --> 00:37:00,060
that you're missing out
on all of the opportunities.

644
00:37:00,070 --> 00:37:01,070
The thing is,

645
00:37:01,550 --> 00:37:03,710
you have a hot figure as well.

646
00:37:06,630 --> 00:37:08,800
Guo, are you done with lunch?

647
00:37:08,810 --> 00:37:11,285
Don't you remember
that we have something important to do?

648
00:37:11,400 --> 00:37:12,280
Let's hurry.

649
00:37:12,457 --> 00:37:13,920
- That's right.
- Larry, I'm sorry.

650
00:37:13,920 --> 00:37:15,110
We'll make a move first. Bye.

651
00:37:15,110 --> 00:37:16,030
What's so important?

652
00:37:20,000 --> 00:37:21,570
What did you guys have for lunch?

653
00:37:21,580 --> 00:37:25,420
(Haowei Food Group)

654
00:37:25,440 --> 00:37:27,320
How do you feel
after joining our company?

655
00:37:28,190 --> 00:37:28,880
It's great.

656
00:37:29,550 --> 00:37:30,960
I feel like everyone here

657
00:37:30,960 --> 00:37:34,857
is in high spirits,
energetic, and peaceful.

658
00:37:35,110 --> 00:37:36,230
Oh my goodness.

659
00:37:36,760 --> 00:37:37,880
I never expected someone

660
00:37:38,110 --> 00:37:39,440
outside of the HR Department

661
00:37:39,440 --> 00:37:41,760
to say something like that.

662
00:37:42,760 --> 00:37:43,360
Is that so?

663
00:37:44,150 --> 00:37:45,230
This is unbelievable.

664
00:37:45,514 --> 00:37:48,342
You know that our company adopts
a last-place elimination system, right?

665
00:37:48,510 --> 00:37:49,110
Yeah.

666
00:37:49,314 --> 00:37:51,070
We have a group-wide
performance assessment.

667
00:37:51,840 --> 00:37:54,000
I don't think our branch
in Shanghai will face the axe.

668
00:37:55,360 --> 00:37:57,510
No matter how good our performances are,

669
00:37:57,550 --> 00:38:00,000
Mr. Xue will hold
a one-to-one conversation

670
00:38:00,150 --> 00:38:01,710
with the worst-performing employee.

671
00:38:03,190 --> 00:38:04,510
One-to-one, you know?

672
00:38:05,550 --> 00:38:06,800
All those who were involved

673
00:38:06,800 --> 00:38:09,960
all resigned from their posts
without any exception.

674
00:38:10,440 --> 00:38:11,840
And, he has a crazy request too.

675
00:38:11,840 --> 00:38:14,542
You have to clean up your desk and leave
before working hours too.

676
00:38:17,550 --> 00:38:19,760
I'm sorry. This is yours, right?

677
00:38:21,920 --> 00:38:22,920
Throw it away for me.

678
00:38:30,050 --> 00:38:32,742
(Marketing Department, Rebecca)
Why do you have Rebecca's employee ID?

679
00:38:32,750 --> 00:38:34,000
I bumped into her this morning.

680
00:38:36,230 --> 00:38:38,960
She's the sacrificial lamb of the
last-place elimination system.

681
00:38:39,114 --> 00:38:41,360
But do employees like me
who were just transferred here

682
00:38:41,590 --> 00:38:43,920
have to participate
in the annual assessment too?

683
00:38:44,510 --> 00:38:45,800
Mr. Xue doesn't care

684
00:38:45,800 --> 00:38:47,400
whether you're a newcomer or not.

685
00:38:47,670 --> 00:38:50,190
And, laying off newcomers

686
00:38:50,190 --> 00:38:51,320
costs the company the least.

687
00:38:51,670 --> 00:38:53,440
Let's take Angela and Orlando

688
00:38:53,440 --> 00:38:55,200
from the Sales Department
as our examples.

689
00:38:55,360 --> 00:38:56,710
The company spent a lot of money

690
00:38:56,710 --> 00:38:58,550
for them to attend
the Haijiang Elite Course.

691
00:38:58,550 --> 00:39:00,800
Laying them off will be
a huge loss for the company.

692
00:39:02,440 --> 00:39:04,960
Lucy, what kind of individuals

693
00:39:04,960 --> 00:39:06,760
are eligible for such courses?

694
00:39:07,800 --> 00:39:09,070
You can attend it too

695
00:39:09,080 --> 00:39:10,500
if you fork out the money yourself.

696
00:39:10,510 --> 00:39:11,710
However, it's too expensive.

697
00:39:11,710 --> 00:39:13,230
Ordinary people can't afford it.

698
00:39:13,880 --> 00:39:16,880
I suggest you try your best
to hit your KPI.

699
00:39:17,280 --> 00:39:18,800
If not, not only will you not get

700
00:39:18,810 --> 00:39:20,150
to attend the course in Haijiang,

701
00:39:20,150 --> 00:39:21,510
but you'll also get the sack.

702
00:39:21,670 --> 00:39:23,670
Is Mr. Xue that terrifying?

703
00:39:23,960 --> 00:39:25,440
Seems like you failed to read the air

704
00:39:25,440 --> 00:39:26,480
in the company

705
00:39:26,480 --> 00:39:28,070
during your first day of work.

706
00:39:28,280 --> 00:39:30,190
Moreover,
you came together with Ms. Chen.

707
00:39:30,320 --> 00:39:31,630
That's not an advantage.

708
00:39:31,640 --> 00:39:33,742
It might cause you
to have a high goal to achieve.

709
00:39:35,150 --> 00:39:37,760
Doesn't that mean
our department is quite dangerous?

710
00:39:38,800 --> 00:39:40,714
You finally
understood the situation, huh?

711
00:39:49,510 --> 00:39:51,800
Excuse me. Is Mr. Xue around?

712
00:39:54,480 --> 00:39:56,880
Emma, I found last year's quotation.

713
00:39:57,000 --> 00:39:57,920
And...

714
00:39:58,590 --> 00:39:59,150
I...

715
00:39:59,857 --> 00:40:00,800
Do you need anything?

716
00:40:01,200 --> 00:40:03,485
Mr. Xue, I'm Xia Guo
from the Marketing Department.

717
00:40:03,485 --> 00:40:05,628
- Ms. Chen wants me to...
- I know. Speak.

718
00:40:05,710 --> 00:40:08,314
Ms. Chen wants me to deliver this to you
so that you can sign it.

719
00:40:08,971 --> 00:40:10,000
Put it on my desk.

720
00:40:11,114 --> 00:40:13,285
I compared this year's quotation
with last year's.

721
00:40:13,510 --> 00:40:14,380
After that, you...

722
00:40:14,380 --> 00:40:15,800
Do you need anything else?

723
00:40:17,840 --> 00:40:19,670
As I need to hurry to the studio,

724
00:40:19,760 --> 00:40:22,342
I have to bring back the signed document
as soon as possible.

725
00:40:23,657 --> 00:40:25,490
You have to bring it back
as soon as possible.

726
00:40:25,510 --> 00:40:27,960
However, I need to review it seriously.

727
00:40:28,880 --> 00:40:30,190
What should we do, then?

728
00:40:31,320 --> 00:40:32,230
You're right.

729
00:40:32,840 --> 00:40:34,000
I'll head out first, then.

730
00:40:37,150 --> 00:40:38,630
I think it's a little different...

731
00:40:38,760 --> 00:40:39,230
Sorry.

732
00:40:39,240 --> 00:40:40,220
- Mr. Xue.
- Last year...

733
00:40:40,230 --> 00:40:43,230
May I know when's the best time for me

734
00:40:43,320 --> 00:40:44,771
to come and retrieve the document?

735
00:40:45,920 --> 00:40:47,760
I'll review it as soon as possible
and hand it

736
00:40:47,760 --> 00:40:49,400
to Ms. Chen myself, okay?

737
00:40:49,960 --> 00:40:51,400
You can proceed with your work now.

738
00:40:52,285 --> 00:40:53,190
Thank you, Mr. Xue.

739
00:40:53,190 --> 00:40:54,285
No, I have to thank you.

740
00:40:56,028 --> 00:40:57,840
- Sorry.
- You don't need to review this.

741
00:40:58,030 --> 00:40:58,480
No.

742
00:40:58,590 --> 00:41:00,840
Did you consider
the previous project I mentioned?

743
00:41:01,920 --> 00:41:03,590
May we have a chat?

744
00:41:04,800 --> 00:41:05,960
Guys,

745
00:41:05,960 --> 00:41:07,800
please follow our page.

746
00:41:08,280 --> 00:41:09,340
It's Link No. 35.

747
00:41:09,360 --> 00:41:10,280
Link No. 35.

748
00:41:10,371 --> 00:41:11,510
Place your order immediately.

749
00:41:11,520 --> 00:41:13,760
Buy your kitchen utensils
and get three items for free!

750
00:41:13,770 --> 00:41:15,910
(This is delicious!)
That's right. Three items for free.

751
00:41:15,920 --> 00:41:17,371
Place your order if you like them.

752
00:41:17,710 --> 00:41:18,280
It's sold out.

753
00:41:18,428 --> 00:41:19,280
It's already sold out.

754
00:41:19,760 --> 00:41:21,320
Three, two, one, the link is closed.

755
00:41:21,320 --> 00:41:22,760
It's selling like hotcakes, huh?

756
00:41:22,760 --> 00:41:23,400
The next item.

757
00:41:23,400 --> 00:41:24,480
Only 2,000 of them, but we

758
00:41:24,480 --> 00:41:25,940
have to stay the entire afternoon.

759
00:41:25,950 --> 00:41:27,480
Xiao Jie placed
our products at the back.

760
00:41:27,480 --> 00:41:29,000
That means our products are popular.

761
00:41:29,280 --> 00:41:30,800
Even so, it doesn't amount to much.

762
00:41:31,150 --> 00:41:33,190
Yesterday, during my live stream,

763
00:41:33,190 --> 00:41:35,630
I had a slice of cake unintentionally.

764
00:41:35,640 --> 00:41:37,020
- Our turn.
- Everyone was asking me

765
00:41:37,030 --> 00:41:38,550
where I bought the cake from.

766
00:41:39,030 --> 00:41:41,440
Today, I'll give you guys
the answer you want.

767
00:41:41,500 --> 00:41:43,400
(Is this cake delicious?)
This is the keto cake,

768
00:41:43,400 --> 00:41:46,360
(Super delicious!)
a product launched by Haowei Food Group.

769
00:41:46,670 --> 00:41:48,710
This cake is made
with plant-based sweeteners.

770
00:41:48,800 --> 00:41:50,900
It's perfect for girls
who are cutting back on sugar.

771
00:41:50,910 --> 00:41:52,630
Right now,
we have 2,000 of them in stock.

772
00:41:52,630 --> 00:41:53,960
Only 2,000 of them.

773
00:41:53,960 --> 00:41:54,960
Post the link.

774
00:41:55,480 --> 00:41:56,150
It's gone.

775
00:41:56,150 --> 00:41:57,400
(I'm ready! Press the link!)

776
00:41:57,400 --> 00:41:58,110
It's gone.

777
00:41:58,228 --> 00:41:59,320
It sold out in a second.

778
00:41:59,320 --> 00:42:00,880
You see? Waiting here was worth it.

779
00:42:02,000 --> 00:42:02,920
I never expected

780
00:42:02,920 --> 00:42:05,480
this cake to be this popular
on our page.

781
00:42:05,800 --> 00:42:07,440
What? You want more?

782
00:42:07,760 --> 00:42:10,400
I'll see if I can request
additional stocks for you guys.

783
00:42:10,885 --> 00:42:12,457
Can we get more of your products?

784
00:42:15,628 --> 00:42:17,060
Xia Guo, add another 8,000 of them.

785
00:42:17,070 --> 00:42:18,400
Don't panic if you fail to buy it.

786
00:42:18,400 --> 00:42:19,400
Let me ask Ms. Chen.

787
00:42:19,400 --> 00:42:20,910
No need.
We're running out of time.

788
00:42:20,920 --> 00:42:22,620
We have to strike while the iron is hot.

789
00:42:22,630 --> 00:42:24,670
Even so, I can't make
the call here. I'll be quick.

790
00:42:25,510 --> 00:42:28,110
Look at the order quantity of this cake.

791
00:42:28,110 --> 00:42:29,230
Guys, don't be impatient.

792
00:42:29,630 --> 00:42:32,760
Dear, you guys
must be quicker next time, okay?

793
00:42:34,000 --> 00:42:36,670
(Hello. The number you have dialed
is unavailable.)

794
00:42:36,857 --> 00:42:38,171
We'll add another 8,000 cakes.

795
00:42:38,240 --> 00:42:39,000
Okay.

796
00:42:39,070 --> 00:42:40,320
Great news!

797
00:42:40,670 --> 00:42:42,710
Haowei Food Group has decided

798
00:42:42,710 --> 00:42:44,550
to sell an additional 8,000 cakes.

799
00:42:44,760 --> 00:42:45,480
My dear...

800
00:42:45,630 --> 00:42:46,880
How could you add to the order?

801
00:42:47,428 --> 00:42:48,860
How could you touch my computer?

802
00:42:48,870 --> 00:42:50,320
It will improve our sales performance.

803
00:42:50,320 --> 00:42:51,109
We must seize it!

804
00:42:51,110 --> 00:42:52,880
The opportunity will be gone
if we consult them.

805
00:42:52,880 --> 00:42:54,510
Even so,
we have to follow the procedures.

806
00:42:54,510 --> 00:42:56,840
And, how would you know
if our warehouse has any ready stocks?

807
00:42:56,840 --> 00:42:58,400
